General.Name: Castro
General.Description: Castro Model Ltd. engages in the retail sale of fashion products, home fashion, fashion accessories, and cosmetics and grooming products through a chain of stores in Israel. The company's products portfolio includes putters and knitwear, jeans, jackets and coats, shirts, shoes, dresses, skirts, lingeries, pajamas and slippers, swimwear, bags and accessories, potters, T-shirts, underwears, cases and garden suits, pants and tights, and bodysuits. It also offers home wear, cushions, blankets, and linen products; carpets and rugs and fragrance and decoration products; bath rugs, towels, and bath accessories; and napkins, cooking accessories, cake stands, realizers, and bowels, as well as gift cards. The company provides its products for women, men, boys, girls, and babies. Castro Model Ltd. is based in Bat Yam, Israel.
General.Address: 31 Ort Israel street, Bat Yam, Israel, 59590
